Minimal system requirements:
>=1.4ghz 64-bit cpu
2GB RAM (ha)
32GB storage (absolute minimum, no roles)
--------------------------------
boot into installation media
select language (laguages are not cross compatible)
select version (standard [core], standard w/desktop, datacenter [core], datacenter w/desktop)
accept uela
upgrade vs custom install
select target disk
install...
set password (warning this is the only password that needs to later be remembered for recovery)
log in as admin for first time
done
